sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Manager
    participant UI as Dashboard UI
    participant Q as Work Queue Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant A as Analytics Engine
    participant N as Notification Service
    participant C as Colegio Rep
    participant P as Perito

    Note over M,P: Work Queue Operations + Analytics Flow

    %% Creation Phase
    M->>UI: Create new Avalúo request
    UI->>Q: POST /avaluos
    Q->>DB: Insert avalúo record
    DB-->>Q: avalúo_id, timestamp
    Q->>A: Log event (creation)
    A->>DB: Update analytics_events

    %% Assignment Phase
    M->>UI: View available Colegios
    UI->>Q: GET /colegios/available
    Q->>DB: Query active Colegios
    Q->>A: Request workload metrics
    A->>DB: Aggregate current workload
    DB-->>A: Workload stats per Colegio
    A-->>Q: Enriched Colegio data
    Q-->>UI: Colegios list with metrics
    UI-->>M: Display workload indicators

    M->>UI: Assign to Colegio X
    UI->>Q: PUT /avaluos/:id/assign
    Q->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    Q->>DB: Update avalúo.colegio_id
    Q->>DB: Insert assignment_log
    Q->>A: Log event (assignment)
    A->>DB: Update real-time metrics
    Q->>DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION

    Q->>N: Trigger notification
    N->>C: Email/Push: New assignment
    Q-->>UI: Assignment confirmed
    UI-->>M: Show success + updated queue

    %% Colegio Internal Assignment
    C->>UI: Login to Colegio dashboard
    UI->>Q: GET /colegios/:id/dashboard
    Q->>DB: Query assigned avalúos
    Q->>A: Request team analytics
    A->>DB: Calculate perito availability
    A->>DB: Calculate workload distribution
    DB-->>A: Team metrics
    A-->>Q: Dashboard data
    Q-->>UI: Pending work + analytics
    UI-->>C: Display queue with charts

    C->>UI: Select Perito for assignment
    UI->>Q: GET /peritos/availability
    Q->>A: Real-time workload check
    A->>DB: Query active_cases per Perito
    DB-->>A: Current assignments
    A-->>Q: Availability matrix
    Q-->>UI: Perito list with capacity

    C->>UI: Assign to Perito Y
    UI->>Q: PUT /avaluos/:id/assign-perito
    Q->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    Q->>DB: Update avalúo.perito_id
    Q->>DB: Update avalúo.status = 'in_progress'
    Q->>DB: Increment peritos.active_cases
    Q->>A: Log event (perito_assignment)
    A->>DB: Update analytics pipeline
    Q->>DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION

    Q->>N: Trigger notification
    N->>P: Notify new case assignment
    Q-->>UI: Assignment success
    UI-->>C: Updated dashboard

    %% Work Progress Tracking
    P->>UI: Update work status
    UI->>Q: PATCH /avaluos/:id/status
    Q->>DB: Update status + timestamp
    Q->>A: Log event (status_change)

    %% Real-time Analytics Update
    A->>DB: Recalculate KPIs
    A->>DB: Update dashboard_cache
    Note over A,DB: SLA tracking<br/>Average completion time<br/>Bottleneck detection

    %% Dashboard Analytics Query
    M->>UI: View analytics dashboard
    UI->>Q: GET /analytics/overview
    Q->>A: Fetch aggregated metrics
    A->>DB: Query analytics_events
    A->>DB: Query avaluos status distribution
    A->>DB: Query workload trends
    DB-->>A: Raw metrics data

    Note over A: Parallel Analytics Processing<br/>- Calculate completion rate<br/>- Calculate avg turnaround time<br/>- Identify bottlenecks<br/>- Generate forecast trends

    A-->>Q: Compiled analytics payload
    Q-->>UI: Dashboard data
    UI-->>M: Render charts & metrics

    %% Completion Phase
    P->>UI: Submit completed Avalúo
    UI->>Q: PUT /avaluos/:id/complete
    Q->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    Q->>DB: Update status = 'completed'
    Q->>DB: Set completion_timestamp
    Q->>DB: Decrement peritos.active_cases
    Q->>A: Log event (completion)

    A->>DB: Calculate SLA compliance
    A->>DB: Update historical metrics
    A->>DB: Trigger quality score calculation
    Q->>DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION

    Q->>N: Notify stakeholders
    N->>M: Case completed notification
    N->>C: Performance update

    Q-->>UI: Success response
    UI-->>P: Confirmation message

    %% Final Analytics Sync
    A->>A: Batch update daily aggregates
    A->>DB: Store processed analytics
    Note over A,DB: End-of-day processing<br/>Historical trends<br/>Performance reports
